Deep Navy Blue — #0D1B2A  deep, authoritative base color that conveys trust and professionalism.

Gold Accent — #FFD700 classic gold that adds a touch of luxury and elegance.

Charcoal Gray — #222222 neutral, sleek color for backgrounds or text, balancing the palette.

